{"tid":1655031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"SCMP：林鄭認為目前回應訴求毫無意義","createTime":"2019-10-15T01:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T04:34:47.000Z","uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":130,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"87fb55d0d8fb9865a22bd4535b0274c4440cf784","tid":1655031,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:11:52.000Z","msg":"《南華早報》引述歐盟內部報告報道稱，特首林鄭月娥告訴歐盟駐香港及澳門代表，重啟政改的討論將需要全國人大的制憲措施，而且目前社會也兩極分化。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥對歐盟駐香港及澳門代表Carmen Cano表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">當前而言回應示威者的訴求毫無意義，因為「你沒法跟暴徒談判(you can't negotiate with the mob)」</span>，報道指，林鄭引述了近期發生的故意破壞和非法堵路事件。反修例活動的五大訴求之一，正是重啟政改。而報道亦指，林鄭撤回逃犯條例訂在示威者眼中是「太少，太遲」。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述的文件，日期是10月8日，文件指，林鄭表示會確保區議會選舉如期於11月24日舉行，但這視乎示威者(But it was &quot;up to protesters&quot;)。報道指，林鄭月娥預計下個月的區議會選舉中建制派將遭受重損失。<br />\n<br />\n而於周三發表的施政報告，報道指，林鄭月娥將側重於土地和住房問題；她又重申對「一國兩制」的信心，但不會包括政治問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1571099248086&amp;issue=20191015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1571099248086%26issue%3D20191015&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9GlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=57fd3a99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1571099248086&amp;issue=20191015</a>"},{"pid":"137291ae2065129e82814c4a230f495a48c2ced7","tid":1655031,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:13:23.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong leader Carrie Lam &lsquo;rules out debate on universal suffrage&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3032911/not-feasible-relaunch-debate-universal-suffrage-now-hong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3032911%2Fnot-feasible-relaunch-debate-universal-suffrage-now-hong&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9GlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=7b42e413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/ho